data.title: 276 - Durgapur Purba - 275 Polling Stations
data.meta_description: 276_Durgapur Purba_275 Polling stations - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document contains a list of 44 polling stations in Durgapur-Purba Assembly Constituency located in buildings such as schools and community centers. Each entry provides the ward number, street, village, pin code, subdivision and district of each polling station location. The specific room numbers where voting will take place are also identified for many of the entries.
